    {
      "id": "bJIM_18SEH6gejqtvq1qm",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -296.67044714550434,
      "y": 6197.466125364077,
      "width": 1372.7364923415798,
      "height": 1405.0000000000002,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b1L",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2122087747,
      "version": 1203,
      "versionNonce": 946071790,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774923331713,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "MDM Selection Criteria & Weights\n\n1. Function Fit Gap (30%)\n   • DCR coverage (creation, update, merging)\n   • Bulk data processing capabilities\n   • Match & merge rule flexibility\n   • Multi-level relationship management\n   • Review & auditing capability\n\n2. Flexibility (25%)\n   • Data import/export/migration tools\n   • Data model extensibility\n   • Integration adaptability\n   • Reporting & analytics support\n   • DevOps & deployment automation\n\n3. Security & Compliance (20%)\n   • Local legal compliance (PIPL/CSL)\n   • In-China data storage capability\n   • Information security & access control\n   • Encryption technology\n   • Security incident response\n\n4. Supportability & Sustainability (15%)\n   • Local technical support & SLA\n   • Vendor development outlook\n   • Upgrade/maintenance manageability\n   • Environmental sustainability\n\n5. Cost & Timeline (10%)\n   • Software licensing & operations cost\n   • Implementation period & resources\n   • Future upgrade/scaling costs\n   • Total cost of ownership (TCO)MDM Selection Criteria & WeightsData Model",
      "fontSize": 33.05882352941177,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "MDM Selection Criteria & Weights\n\n1. Function Fit Gap (30%)\n   • DCR coverage (creation, update, merging)\n   • Bulk data processing capabilities\n   • Match & merge rule flexibility\n   • Multi-level relationship management\n   • Review & auditing capability\n\n2. Flexibility (25%)\n   • Data import/export/migration tools\n   • Data model extensibility\n   • Integration adaptability\n   • Reporting & analytics support\n   • DevOps & deployment automation\n\n3. Security & Compliance (20%)\n   • Local legal compliance (PIPL/CSL)\n   • In-China data storage capability\n   • Information security & access control\n   • Encryption technology\n   • Security incident response\n\n4. Supportability & Sustainability (15%)\n   • Local technical support & SLA\n   • Vendor development outlook\n   • Upgrade/maintenance manageability\n   • Environmental sustainability\n\n5. Cost & Timeline (10%)\n   • Software licensing & operations cost\n   • Implementation period & resources\n   • Future upgrade/scaling costs\n   • Total cost of ownership (TCO)MDM Selection Criteria & WeightsData Model",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
