      "seed": 1445575437,
      "version": 989,
      "versionNonce": 888532557,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1756965580574,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Different template for different\ntype of DCR:\n1. HCP Create Batch Review\n   ** if the DCR matched suspect\nduplicates, duplicate HCP\ninformation (name, department,\nhospital) shall display\n2. HCP Update Batch Review\n   ** new value vs. old value\n3. HCP Merge Batch Review\n   ** new value vs. old value\n   ** winner HCP, loser HCP\n   ** Final Winner HCP",
      "fontSize": 20.69135802469135,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Different template for different type of DCR:\n1. HCP Create Batch Review\n   ** if the DCR matched suspect duplicates, duplicate HCP information (name, department, hospital) shall display\n2. HCP Update Batch Review\n   ** new value vs. old value\n3. HCP Merge Batch Review\n   ** new value vs. old value\n   ** winner HCP, loser HCP\n   ** Final Winner HCP",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
