      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "权重分配 rationale（适用理由）：",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "权重分配 rationale（适用理由）：",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "sSHVzGGyl2dFXc1gzKMyL",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1522.9418023352969,
      "y": 9028.159091449514,
      "width": 784,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b9C",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 71747114,
      "version": 3,
      "versionNonce": 794234550,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1757380005173,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "功能契合度（30%）：直接决定能否满足业务核心需求，对于医药行业主数据管理，业务\n适配第一优先级。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "功能契合度（30%）：直接决定能否满足业务核心需求，对于医药行业主数据管理，业务适配第一优先级。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "BP3dSC_oNtDF-1y2KExN_",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1518.0017998938906,
      "y": 9123.159091449514,
      "width": 793.8800048828125,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b9D",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1561299318,
      "version": 3,
      "versionNonce": 1617878954,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1757380005173,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "灵活性（20%）：主数据系统必须与现有与未来IT体系灵活对接，后台、模型、集成的扩\n展能力极其关键。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "灵活性（20%）：主数据系统必须与现有与未来IT体系灵活对接，后台、模型、集成的扩展能力极其关键。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "aL85jOc7Tt7g1XHl9B5Y4",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1533.6318658118594,
      "y": 9230.659091449514,
      "width": 762.619873046875,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b9E",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1688236266,
      "version": 3,
      "versionNonce": 1244645366,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1757380005173,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "安全与合规（20%）：中国区合规（如PIPL/CSL）要求非常高，数据安全不可妥协。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "安全与合规（20%）：中国区合规（如PIPL/CSL）要求非常高，数据安全不可妥协。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "VHOUB_Xsr60FsOD5VlSSB",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1528.0318291907656,
      "y": 9288.159091449514,
      "width": 773.8199462890625,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b9F",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 143321782,
      "version": 3,
      "versionNonce": 126442090,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1757380005173,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "可支持&可持续（15%）：长期运维保障与本地化服务决定了系统生命周期内的风险和效\n率。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "可支持&可持续（15%）：长期运维保障与本地化服务决定了系统生命周期内的风险和效率。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "6B5fnM3VZamlIiVKbrneI",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1517.5518487220156,
      "y": 9383.159091449514,
      "width": 794.7799072265625,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b9G",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1240908714,
      "version": 3,
      "versionNonce": 337598774,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1757380005173,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "成本&周期（15%）：药企重视ROI，成本和实施资源需合理控制，但一般不会牺牲前面几\n个维度的本质质量。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "成本&周期（15%）：药企重视ROI，成本和实施资源需合理控制，但一般不会牺牲前面几个维度的本质质量。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "QE6uDYtnr33jQVsvgQ9iH",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1874.9418023352969,
      "y": 9490.659091449514,
      "width": 80,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b9H",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 143139830,
      "version": 3,
      "versionNonce": 1124498730,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1757380005173,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "应用建议",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "应用建议",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "1iYtX3ExmQ8umeausMpHk",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1521.6418450599062,
      "y": 9513.159091449514,
      "width": 786.5999145507812,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b9I",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1047838314,
      "version": 3,
      "versionNonce": 881508982,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1757380005173,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "联合IT、业务、合规部门共同review和确认权重，充分平衡战略、现实、未来发展等多方\n诉求。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "联合IT、业务、合规部门共同review和确认权重，充分平衡战略、现实、未来发展等多方诉求。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "A2s5hBzFaZzNblertIPj7",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1530.9618218665469,
      "y": 9608.159091449514,
      "width": 767.9599609375,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b9J",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 520893750,
      "version": 3,
      "versionNonce": 1079068650,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1757380005173,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "如合规性为短板可进一步上调“安全与合规”权重；如预算极严可适当提升“成本&周期”至\n20%，但一般不建议高于功能和合规。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "如合规性为短板可进一步上调“安全与合规”权重；如预算极严可适当提升“成本&周期”至20%，但一般不建议高于功能和合规。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "wrV8-4KnsR_sD1CboH1z1",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1704.9418023352969,
      "y": 9715.659091449514,
      "width": 420,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b9K",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1323655466,
      "version": 3,
      "versionNonce": 506921910,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1757380005173,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "最终权重建议多方共识后形成正式选型评分表。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "最终权重建议多方共识后形成正式选型评分表。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "Nfmr6v7xzXmt7nXcDTFcp",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1514.9418023352969,
      "y": 9773.159091449514,
      "width": 800,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b9L",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 92020342,
      "version": 3,
      "versionNonce": 1198832298,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1757380005173,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "这个建议适合于医药、跨国等高标准行业中国区项目，兼顾了业务、合规、长期演进和投入\n产出效率。如需针对诺华内部实际情况微调，也可分阶段动态调整。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "这个建议适合于医药、跨国等高标准行业中国区项目，兼顾了业务、合规、长期演进和投入产出效率。如需针对诺华内部实际情况微调，也可分阶段动态调整。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
