      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1757380308723,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "权重分配 rationale（适用理由）：",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "权重分配 rationale（适用理由）：",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "Ux9jBmobLymTZ7ygPt1nP",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1747.9418023352969,
      "y": 10253.159091449514,
      "width": 784,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bA4",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1513737270,
      "version": 3,
      "versionNonce": 2055176426,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1757380308723,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "功能契合度（30%）：直接决定能否满足业务核心需求，对于医药行业主数据管理，业务\n适配第一优先级。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "功能契合度（30%）：直接决定能否满足业务核心需求，对于医药行业主数据管理，业务适配第一优先级。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "aH39JCNcIzYp8TimpOFNE",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1743.0017998938906,
      "y": 10348.159091449514,
      "width": 793.8800048828125,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bA5",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1480636970,
      "version": 3,
      "versionNonce": 266656438,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1757380308723,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "灵活性（20%）：主数据系统必须与现有与未来IT体系灵活对接，后台、模型、集成的扩\n展能力极其关键。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "灵活性（20%）：主数据系统必须与现有与未来IT体系灵活对接，后台、模型、集成的扩展能力极其关键。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "HrOBZKBzMzA6T_g0EOgsf",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1758.6318658118594,
      "y": 10455.659091449514,
      "width": 762.619873046875,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bA6",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1423889782,
      "version": 3,
      "versionNonce": 1903416234,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1757380308723,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "安全与合规（20%）：中国区合规（如PIPL/CSL）要求非常高，数据安全不可妥协。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "安全与合规（20%）：中国区合规（如PIPL/CSL）要求非常高，数据安全不可妥协。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "F58E9QwCSzgpzYoxKVS3R",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1753.0318291907656,
      "y": 10513.159091449514,
      "width": 773.8199462890625,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bA7",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 222029034,
      "version": 3,
      "versionNonce": 1864635382,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1757380308723,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "可支持&可持续（15%）：长期运维保障与本地化服务决定了系统生命周期内的风险和效\n率。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "可支持&可持续（15%）：长期运维保障与本地化服务决定了系统生命周期内的风险和效率。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "11DQPnJK0ZycKs5DhSAWu",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1742.5518487220156,
      "y": 10608.159091449514,
      "width": 794.7799072265625,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bA8",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1620096694,
      "version": 3,
      "versionNonce": 332385898,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1757380308723,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "成本&周期（15%）：药企重视ROI，成本和实施资源需合理控制，但一般不会牺牲前面几\n个维度的本质质量。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "成本&周期（15%）：药企重视ROI，成本和实施资源需合理控制，但一般不会牺牲前面几个维度的本质质量。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "hQrffRG9f1yEj8EeTWKey",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2099.941802335297,
      "y": 10715.659091449514,
      "width": 80,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bA9",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 922990506,
      "version": 3,
      "versionNonce": 749348150,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1757380308723,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "应用建议",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "应用建议",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "MpBhZFgw3bHXPdbuNAqot",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1746.6418450599062,
      "y": 10738.159091449514,
      "width": 786.5999145507812,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bAA",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1978953718,
      "version": 3,
      "versionNonce": 1717465386,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1757380308723,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "联合IT、业务、合规部门共同review和确认权重，充分平衡战略、现实、未来发展等多方\n诉求。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "联合IT、业务、合规部门共同review和确认权重，充分平衡战略、现实、未来发展等多方诉求。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "nAWuyJq6qXLyvfJsizcqs",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1755.9618218665469,
      "y": 10833.159091449514,
      "width": 767.9599609375,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bAB",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1707291242,
      "version": 3,
      "versionNonce": 165416566,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1757380308723,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "如合规性为短板可进一步上调“安全与合规”权重；如预算极严可适当提升“成本&周期”至\n20%，但一般不建议高于功能和合规。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "如合规性为短板可进一步上调“安全与合规”权重；如预算极严可适当提升“成本&周期”至20%，但一般不建议高于功能和合规。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "3KOr6E-vUWX4MVoGooadR",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1929.9418023352969,
      "y": 10940.659091449514,
      "width": 420,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bAC",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 823066934,
      "version": 3,
      "versionNonce": 478854122,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1757380308723,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "最终权重建议多方共识后形成正式选型评分表。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "最终权重建议多方共识后形成正式选型评分表。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "ZWmcCdtkPB525sqgD0vpw",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1739.9418023352969,
      "y": 10998.159091449514,
      "width": 800,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bAD",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1816483114,
      "version": 3,
      "versionNonce": 1400819638,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1757380308723,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "这个建议适合于医药、跨国等高标准行业中国区项目，兼顾了业务、合规、长期演进和投入\n产出效率。如需针对诺华内部实际情况微调，也可分阶段动态调整。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "这个建议适合于医药、跨国等高标准行业中国区项目，兼顾了业务、合规、长期演进和投入产出效率。如需针对诺华内部实际情况微调，也可分阶段动态调整。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
