      "seed": 1987268778,
      "version": 3,
      "versionNonce": 1995812982,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1757380339233,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "功能契合度（30%）：直接决定能否满足业务核心需求，对于医药行业主数据管理，业务\n适配第一优先级。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "功能契合度（30%）：直接决定能否满足业务核心需求，对于医药行业主数据管理，业务适配第一优先级。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "GJXJPmED2ji2p2L6Gd0j7",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 558.0017998938906,
      "y": 8918.159091449514,
      "width": 793.8800048828125,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bAx",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1504110326,
      "version": 3,
      "versionNonce": 1624521194,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1757380339233,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "灵活性（20%）：主数据系统必须与现有与未来IT体系灵活对接，后台、模型、集成的扩\n展能力极其关键。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "灵活性（20%）：主数据系统必须与现有与未来IT体系灵活对接，后台、模型、集成的扩展能力极其关键。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "TSavRLv7g0VMkyuGZuFor",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 573.6318658118594,
      "y": 9025.659091449514,
      "width": 762.619873046875,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bAy",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 634891114,
      "version": 3,
      "versionNonce": 1897148854,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1757380339233,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "安全与合规（20%）：中国区合规（如PIPL/CSL）要求非常高，数据安全不可妥协。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "安全与合规（20%）：中国区合规（如PIPL/CSL）要求非常高，数据安全不可妥协。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "xRjgo_BYfEGbYELQ5sNvO",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 568.0318291907656,
      "y": 9083.159091449514,
      "width": 773.8199462890625,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bAz",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 89823286,
      "version": 3,
      "versionNonce": 2127129770,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1757380339233,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "可支持&可持续（15%）：长期运维保障与本地化服务决定了系统生命周期内的风险和效\n率。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "可支持&可持续（15%）：长期运维保障与本地化服务决定了系统生命周期内的风险和效率。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "m4YDq9IzbLYQw9euzUsAd",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 557.5518487220156,
      "y": 9178.159091449514,
      "width": 794.7799072265625,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bB0",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 90353194,
      "version": 3,
      "versionNonce": 1045465846,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1757380339233,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "成本&周期（15%）：药企重视ROI，成本和实施资源需合理控制，但一般不会牺牲前面几\n个维度的本质质量。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "成本&周期（15%）：药企重视ROI，成本和实施资源需合理控制，但一般不会牺牲前面几个维度的本质质量。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "BpEd5Sl38m-5wy6B0r3VA",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 914.9418023352969,
      "y": 9285.659091449514,
      "width": 80,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bB1",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2047222134,
      "version": 3,
      "versionNonce": 1963607914,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1757380339233,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "应用建议",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "应用建议",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "r8b1l06LYj1APNoqY72k2",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 561.6418450599062,
      "y": 9308.159091449514,
      "width": 786.5999145507812,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bB2",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 704600298,
      "version": 3,
      "versionNonce": 1831844918,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1757380339233,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "联合IT、业务、合规部门共同review和确认权重，充分平衡战略、现实、未来发展等多方\n诉求。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "联合IT、业务、合规部门共同review和确认权重，充分平衡战略、现实、未来发展等多方诉求。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "Er98-P9lslGpd5M6KSS4f",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 570.9618218665469,
      "y": 9403.159091449514,
      "width": 767.9599609375,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bB3",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2062451382,
      "version": 3,
      "versionNonce": 199346730,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1757380339233,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "如合规性为短板可进一步上调“安全与合规”权重；如预算极严可适当提升“成本&周期”至\n20%，但一般不建议高于功能和合规。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "如合规性为短板可进一步上调“安全与合规”权重；如预算极严可适当提升“成本&周期”至20%，但一般不建议高于功能和合规。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "bvlGq6xvz5i8hGQUKmL0T",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 744.9418023352969,
      "y": 9510.659091449514,
      "width": 420,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bB4",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1396222890,
      "version": 3,
      "versionNonce": 1939260790,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1757380339233,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "最终权重建议多方共识后形成正式选型评分表。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "最终权重建议多方共识后形成正式选型评分表。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "95Zw3g6W1ts97unMLE5Dq",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 554.9418023352969,
      "y": 9568.159091449514,
      "width": 800,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bB5",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 448314358,
      "version": 3,
      "versionNonce": 1245377770,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1757380339233,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "这个建议适合于医药、跨国等高标准行业中国区项目，兼顾了业务、合规、长期演进和投入\n产出效率。如需针对诺华内部实际情况微调，也可分阶段动态调整。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "这个建议适合于医药、跨国等高标准行业中国区项目，兼顾了业务、合规、长期演进和投入产出效率。如需针对诺华内部实际情况微调，也可分阶段动态调整。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "a8XEeAgOG0M8kPwEz9896",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1562.4418023352969,
      "y": 4765.659091449514,
      "width": 310.995849609375,
      "height": 35,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bB6",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1864276918,
      "version": 43,
      "versionNonce": 732332278,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1757381217475,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "MDM Selection Criteria",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "MDM Selection Criteria",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "QHXO7ykz5-2IU2KjRlL7i",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 869.3862467797417,
      "y": 7365.936869227291,
      "width": 385.959716796875,
      "height": 600,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bB7",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1285490102,
      "version": 186,
      "versionNonce": 1865889002,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1757381262934,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1. Function Fit Gap (30%)\n   • Business requirement alignment\n   • Core MDM capabilities coverage\n   • Integration readiness\n\n2. Flexibility (20%)\n   • Customization options\n   • Scalability potential\n   • Vendor roadmap alignment\n\n3. Security & Compliance (20%)\n   • Data governance features\n   • Regulatory compliance support\n   • Security architecture\n\n4. Supportability & Sustainability (15%)\n   • Vendor support quality\n   • Community & documentation\n   • Long-term viability\n\n5. Cost & Timeline (15%)\n   • Total cost of ownership\n   • Implementation timeline\n   • Resource requirements",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. Function Fit Gap (30%)\n   • Business requirement alignment\n   • Core MDM capabilities coverage\n   • Integration readiness\n\n2. Flexibility (20%)\n   • Customization options\n   • Scalability potential\n   • Vendor roadmap alignment\n\n3. Security & Compliance (20%)\n   • Data governance features\n   • Regulatory compliance support\n   • Security architecture\n\n4. Supportability & Sustainability (15%)\n   • Vendor support quality\n   • Community & documentation\n   • Long-term viability\n\n5. Cost & Timeline (15%)\n   • Total cost of ownership\n   • Implementation timeline\n   • Resource requirements",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "AZObUmSwe8ogAV3MdH0gN",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 6617.16402455752,
      "y": 6102.047980338402,
      "width": 2016.3583984375,
      "height": 1875,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bB8",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1455834474,
      "version": 66,
      "versionNonce": 1568135222,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1757380972473,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "SELECTION CRITERIA\n\n1. FUNCTION FIT GAP\n• DCR (Data Change Request) coverage (creation, update, merging for HCO/HCP/relationships)\n• Bulk data processing capabilities (bulk DCR, mass review)\n• Match & merge rule flexibility and accuracy\n• Multi-level/multi-entity (HCO/HCP) relationship management\nSELECTION CRITERIA\n\n1. FUNCTION FIT GAP\n• DCR (Data Change Request) coverage (creation, update, merging for HCO/HCP/relationships)\n• Bulk data processing capabilities (bulk DCR, mass review)\n• Match & merge rule flexibility and accuracy\n• Multi-level/multi-entity (HCO/HCP) relationship management\n• Review & auditing capability\n\n2. FLEXIBILITY\n• Rich and easy-to-use data import/export/migration tools\n• Extensibility of the data model (attributes & entities customization)\n• Integration adaptability with current IT/enterprise systems (API, event-driven, legacy & modern)\n• Reporting & analytics support (custom reports, data visualization)\n• DevOps & deployment automation support (CI/CD toolchain, scripts)\n\n3. SECURITY & COMPLIANCE\n• Local legal compliance support (PIPL/CSL and other Chinese data laws)\n• Capability for in-China data storage & localization\n• Information security and access control (role granularity, permission levels, audit tracing)\n• Encryption technology/compliant interfaces (transit & at-rest encryption, compliant APIs)\n• Security incident response\n\n4. SUPPORTABILITY & SUSTAINABILITY\n• Local technical support & service level (SLA, onsite team, emergency handling)\n• Vendor development outlook & stability (partner ecosystem, product maturity)\n• Manageability of upgrades and maintenance (easy upgrade, patch management)\n• Environmental sustainability commitments (Green IT, eco impact)\n\n5. COST & TIMELINE\n• Software licensing and ongoing operations cost\n• Implementation period and resource requirements\n• Costs for future upgrade/scaling & secondary dev\n• Total cost of ownership (TCO)/ROI estimation\nSELECTION CRITERIA\n\n1. FUNCTION FIT GAP\n• DCR (Data Change Request) coverage (creation, update, merging for HCO/HCP/relationships)\n• Bulk data processing capabilities (bulk DCR, mass review)\n• Match & merge rule flexibility and accuracy\n• Multi-level/multi-entity (HCO/HCP) relationship management\n• Review & auditing capability\n\n2. FLEXIBILITY\n• Rich and easy-to-use data import/export/migration tools\n• Extensibility of the data model (attributes & entities customization)\n• Integration adaptability with current IT/enterprise systems (API, event-driven, legacy & modern)\n• Reporting & analytics support (custom reports, data visualization)\n• DevOps & deployment automation support (CI/CD toolchain, scripts)\n\n3. SECURITY & COMPLIANCE\n• Local legal compliance support (PIPL/CSL and other Chinese data laws)\n• Capability for in-China data storage & localization\n• Information security and access control (role granularity, permission levels, audit tracing)\n• Encryption technology/compliant interfaces (transit & at-rest encryption, compliant APIs)\n• Security incident response\n\n4. SUPPORTABILITY & SUSTAINABILITY\n• Local technical support & service level (SLA, onsite team, emergency handling)\n• Vendor development outlook & stability (partner ecosystem, product maturity)\n• Manageability of upgrades and maintenance (easy upgrade, patch management)\n• Environmental sustainability commitments (Green IT, eco impact)\n\n5. COST & TIMELINE\n• Software licensing and ongoing operations cost\n• Implementation period and resource requirements\n• Costs for future upgrade/scaling & secondary dev\nMDM Selection Criteria & Weights• Total cost of ownership (TCO)/ROI estimation• Customization difficulty & cost transparency• Customization difficulty & cost transparency• Review & auditing capability",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "SELECTION CRITERIA\n\n1. FUNCTION FIT GAP\n• DCR (Data Change Request) coverage (creation, update, merging for HCO/HCP/relationships)\n• Bulk data processing capabilities (bulk DCR, mass review)\n• Match & merge rule flexibility and accuracy\n• Multi-level/multi-entity (HCO/HCP) relationship management\nSELECTION CRITERIA\n\n1. FUNCTION FIT GAP\n• DCR (Data Change Request) coverage (creation, update, merging for HCO/HCP/relationships)\n• Bulk data processing capabilities (bulk DCR, mass review)\n• Match & merge rule flexibility and accuracy\n• Multi-level/multi-entity (HCO/HCP) relationship management\n• Review & auditing capability\n\n2. FLEXIBILITY\n• Rich and easy-to-use data import/export/migration tools\n• Extensibility of the data model (attributes & entities customization)\n• Integration adaptability with current IT/enterprise systems (API, event-driven, legacy & modern)\n• Reporting & analytics support (custom reports, data visualization)\n• DevOps & deployment automation support (CI/CD toolchain, scripts)\n\n3. SECURITY & COMPLIANCE\n• Local legal compliance support (PIPL/CSL and other Chinese data laws)\n• Capability for in-China data storage & localization\n• Information security and access control (role granularity, permission levels, audit tracing)\n• Encryption technology/compliant interfaces (transit & at-rest encryption, compliant APIs)\n• Security incident response\n\n4. SUPPORTABILITY & SUSTAINABILITY\n• Local technical support & service level (SLA, onsite team, emergency handling)\n• Vendor development outlook & stability (partner ecosystem, product maturity)\n• Manageability of upgrades and maintenance (easy upgrade, patch management)\n• Environmental sustainability commitments (Green IT, eco impact)\n\n5. COST & TIMELINE\n• Software licensing and ongoing operations cost\n• Implementation period and resource requirements\n• Costs for future upgrade/scaling & secondary dev\n• Total cost of ownership (TCO)/ROI estimation\nSELECTION CRITERIA\n\n1. FUNCTION FIT GAP\n• DCR (Data Change Request) coverage (creation, update, merging for HCO/HCP/relationships)\n• Bulk data processing capabilities (bulk DCR, mass review)\n• Match & merge rule flexibility and accuracy\n• Multi-level/multi-entity (HCO/HCP) relationship management\n• Review & auditing capability\n\n2. FLEXIBILITY\n• Rich and easy-to-use data import/export/migration tools\n• Extensibility of the data model (attributes & entities customization)\n• Integration adaptability with current IT/enterprise systems (API, event-driven, legacy & modern)\n• Reporting & analytics support (custom reports, data visualization)\n• DevOps & deployment automation support (CI/CD toolchain, scripts)\n\n3. SECURITY & COMPLIANCE\n• Local legal compliance support (PIPL/CSL and other Chinese data laws)\n• Capability for in-China data storage & localization\n• Information security and access control (role granularity, permission levels, audit tracing)\n• Encryption technology/compliant interfaces (transit & at-rest encryption, compliant APIs)\n• Security incident response\n\n4. SUPPORTABILITY & SUSTAINABILITY\n• Local technical support & service level (SLA, onsite team, emergency handling)\n• Vendor development outlook & stability (partner ecosystem, product maturity)\n• Manageability of upgrades and maintenance (easy upgrade, patch management)\n• Environmental sustainability commitments (Green IT, eco impact)\n\n5. COST & TIMELINE\n• Software licensing and ongoing operations cost\n• Implementation period and resource requirements\n• Costs for future upgrade/scaling & secondary dev\nMDM Selection Criteria & Weights• Total cost of ownership (TCO)/ROI estimation• Customization difficulty & cost transparency• Customization difficulty & cost transparency• Review & auditing capability",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
